  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meowmewbug is a relaxing and fun idle game. By tapping the magic circle in the center of the scene, you can summon various meowmewbugs with unique appearances and settings. Collecting the paw balls dropped by the meowmewbugs in the scene allows you to unlock more styles of scenes, interesting functions, classic mini-games, and summon even more meowmewbugs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244090/extras/ee2dcc1e782fc2ec293a1f0986b20be7.avif?t=1728457428\" width=462 height=174 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tap on the Q-bouncing magic circle to summon adorable Meowmews!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Come out, ultra-rare Meowmews!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244090/extras/2b165b6caa79084e2f05396f39fac9d7.avif?t=1728457428\" width=300 height=200 /></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > The super stress-relieving collection of paw balls! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let go of that paw ball, let me at it! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244090/extras/c8e91ee7f2cee1c21e1546956a568c4b.avif?t=1728457428\" width=300 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 70+ cute, fun, and unique Meowmews! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lovely appearances, unique settings, warm and amusing dialogues, and plenty of memes. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244090/extras/278b6c394ddd6a3c8111e213014f5ad5.avif?t=1728457428\" width=300 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 10+ classic mini-games and features! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scratch cards, 2048, electronic wooden fish... <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244090/extras/35e528d075d811f6a51eab557f98ab3b.avif?t=1728457428\" width=300 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > More surprises! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special events during special times?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More content is continuously being updated.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244090/extras/c80a046ef338b2f62ed46b6b865ad789.avif?t=1728457428\" width=300 height=200 /></span>",
